#!/bin/bash
set -x

ARTIFACTORY_USERNAME=${p:component/ARTIFACTORY_USERNAME}
ARTIFACTORY_PASSWORD=${p:component/ARTIFACTORY_PASSWORD}
APPD_FID_USER=${p:environment/APPD_FID_USER}
APPD_FID_GROUP=${p:environment/APPD_FID_GROUP}
APPD_EXTN_NAME=${p:APPD_EXTN_NAME}

function install_extn
{
    echo "Downloading RPM ${EXTN_PKG_VERSION}.rpm from Artifactory..."
    
    curl -k -u ${ARTIFACTORY_USERNAME}:${ARTIFACTORY_PASSWORD} "$ARTIFACTORY_PATH/${EXTN_PKG_VERSION}.rpm" --output "/var/tmp/${EXTN_PKG_VERSION}.rpm"

    rpm --force -ih /var/tmp/$EXTN_PKG_VERSION.rpm --relocate /Owner=/$APPD_FID_USER --relocate /Group=/$APPD_FID_GROUP

    #Validate Installation
    EXTN_RPM_VERSION=`rpm -qa | grep $APPD_EXTN_NAME`
    
    if [ -n $EXTN_RPM_VERSION ]
    then
        echo "$APPD_EXTN_NAME Version $EXTN_RPM_VERSION is installed successfully on the server"
        rm -rf /var/tmp/$EXTN_RPM_VERSION.rpm
    else
        echo "Installation didn't complete properly"
        exit 1
    fi
}

if [ "$APPD_EXTN_NAME" == "appdnginxmonitorextension" ]
then
    ARTIFACTORY_PATH=https://artifactrepository.citigroup.net/artifactory/yum-cto-dev-local/cate-citicloud-apm-149931/appd_apm/rhel6-x86_64
    EXTN_PKG_VERSION=appdnginxmonitorextension-1.0-A0.x86_64
fi

curl -k -u ${ARTIFACTORY_USERNAME}:${ARTIFACTORY_PASSWORD} "$ARTIFACTORY_PATH/${EXTN_PKG_VERSION}.rpm" --output "/var/tmp/${EXTN_PKG_VERSION}.rpm"
    
# Check if Extention is already present on the server
IS_EXTN_INSTALLED=$(rpm -qa | grep $APPD_EXTN_NAME | wc -l)

if [ $IS_EXTN_INSTALLED -eq 0 ]
then
    echo "No $APPD_EXTN_NAME Version is currently present on the server. Proceeding with fresh Installattion...."
    install_extn
else
    CURR_EXTN_RPM_VERSION=`rpm -qa | grep  $APPD_EXTN_NAME`
    if [ $CURR_EXTN_RPM_VERSION = $EXTN_PKG_VERSION ]
    then
        echo "$APPD_EXTN_NAME Version $EXTN_PKG_VERSION is already present on the server"
    else
        rpm -e $CURR_EXTN_RPM_VERSION
        echo "Old $APPD_EXTN_NAME version $CURR_EXTN_RPM_VERSION has been Un-installed. Proceeding with new version Installattion...."
        install_extn
    fi
fi

    curl -k -u ${ARTIFACTORY_USERNAME}:${ARTIFACTORY_PASSWORD} "${ARTIFACTORY_URL}/${JA_PKG_VERSION}.rpm" --output "/var/tmp/${JA_PKG_VERSION}.rpm"

    if [ -n $JA_RPM_VERSION ]

        echo "Java Agent Version $JA_RPM_VERSION is installed successfully on the server"
        rm -rf /var/tmp/$JA_RPM_VERSION.rpm
    else
        echo "Installation didn't complete properly"
        exit 1
    fi

    CURR_JA_RPM_VERSION=`rpm -qa | grep  appdjvagent`

    fi
fi

properties.scriptBody:
#!/bin/bash
export USED_AGENT=uDeploy_Agent_RHEL_7.0.3.2_20200715_v17
export USED_AGENT_VER=${USED_AGENT}_cs
export COMPONENT_DATA_DIR=/opt/UCD3_agent_installation_component
export COMPONENT_VER_DIR=$COMPONENT_DATA_DIR/$USED_AGENT_VER
export INSTALL_FILE_NAME=install_ucd3_agent
[ -f $COMPONENT_VER_DIR/$INSTALL_FILE_NAME.tar ] && echo "Tar already exists" && find $COMPONENT_DATA_DIR -print && exit 0
echo "Copy from /net/stealth agent installation tar"
mkdir -p $COMPONENT_VER_DIR
cp -n /net/stealth/export1/home1.localhost/sw/Linux/$USED_AGENT.tar $COMPONENT_VER_DIR
mv $COMPONENT_VER_DIR/$USED_AGENT.tar $COMPONENT_VER_DIR/$INSTALL_FILE_NAME.tar
echo "List $COMPONENT_DATA_DIR for troubleshooting"
find $COMPONENT_DATA_DIR -print
